Functions for working with XML versions of the PSMV

Calculate application rates for active ingredients

Data objects for working with XML versions of the PSMV

Path to the directory where the published XML versions of the PSMV are stored
units_convertible_to_g_per_ha
Product application rate units convertible to grams active substance per hectare
